message.content: cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MED, cs.NEURON - This paper involves the use of Convolutional Neural Networks for image analysis and medical diagnosis, which falls under the categories of computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper focuses on medical applications and specifically cardiovascular diseases, which could place it under the categories of medical imaging (cs.MED) and neural networks (cs.NEURON).
